.SH NAME
CWE\-20 \- Improper Input Validation
.SH RANK
2025 CWE Top 25 rank: \fB#18\fR (2024 rank: 12).
.SH CLASSIFICATION
Class: Validation.
.SH DESCRIPTION
Input is received but not validated (or wrongly validated) for the properties needed for safe processing. A broad root cause feeding many other weaknesses; malformed, out\-of\-range or wrong\-type data reaches sensitive logic.
.SH MITIGATION
Validate every input on the server against an explicit spec: type, range, length, format and allowed set (allow\-list, not deny\-list). Reject invalid input rather than sanitising it. Schema validators make this systematic.
